metadata.name: Soundverse Jukeboxes #1
metadata.description:
Join us on a musical adventure through the Soundverse! 

The Sound King has created 2500 Soundverse Jukeboxes to orbit the Soundverse, protecting it from the vacuum of space and maintaining harmony in their world. 

You can help by verifying your token, which grants access to streaming royalties, chapter features in the Soundverse Lore, custom songs, airdrops, and much more. 

Plus, join our exclusive Soundverse Private Chat on Discord for weekly giveaways, contests, private music NFT drops, and more. 

Explore all the songs within the jukeboxes at https://open.spotify.com/playlist/5Uv8OktLGhWUcFFcgg7TJ2?si=6bbf11b9eb2c42f7 

and join the Discord community at https://discord.gg/cJWABUmHeX. 

Let's gear up and embark on this exciting musical journey together!
